ext-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3","children":"Do customers mind talking to AI instead of a human?"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-white/70 leading-relaxed","children":"Most customers do not realise it is AI. Modern AI receptionists sound natural and professional. Customers care about getting their problem solved quickly, not who answers the phone. Speed and professionalism matter more than human vs AI."}]]}],["$","div","faq-4",{"className":"bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-6","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3","children":"Can I afford a call answering service as a one-man band?"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-white/70 leading-relaxed","children":"Whoza.ai costs £59 per month. That is less than one heating callout. If you miss even one job per month, you lose more than the service costs. Most tradespeople recover 3-5 jobs in their first week. The question is not whether you can afford it. It is whether you can afford to keep missing calls."}]]}]]}]]}]
